vote.title: A resolution authorizing the conveyance of an easement for a tract of land containing approximately 3,131 square feet to Oncor Electric Delivery Company, LLC for the construction, maintenance and use of power lines and electric transformer facilities across City-owned land located near the intersection of Greenville Avenue and Forest Lane - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
